    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_hull_299699",
        "quote": "The HoLee model was the first term structure model. I remember reading their paper soon after it was published and as it was fairly different from many of the other papers that I had read, I had to read it quite a few times. I realized that it was a really important paper.",
